nodes.text: The year 3633 BBY was a period of galactic history. That year, the Jedi Choza Raabat was found on a planet in Wild Space by a Zakuul scouting party. Raabat had been stranded for a decade, and was forced to commandeer the ship after the Zakuulans tried to kill him.
